StoredProcedureOraclev10g.name: INSERTDEGREE
StoredProcedureOraclev10g.source: CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE GRUPO10.INSERTDEGREE(pDegreeName IN VARCHAR2, pLength IN NUMBER,&lt;br/&gt;pDegreePrerequisites IN VARCHAR2, pIDFaculty IN NUMBER) AS&lt;br/&gt;BEGIN&lt;br/&gt; INSERT INTO Degree_table&lt;br/&gt; VALUES(Degree_obj(seqDegree.Nextval, pDegreeName, pLength, pDegreePrerequisites, pIDFaculty));&lt;br/&gt; COMMIT;&lt;br/&gt;END insertDegree;
